import { PatientApi } from "../../client/backend-api/patient" import { useUser } from "../../context/user-context" import classes from "./styles.module.css" import {useEffect, useState} from "react"; import { NotificationManager } from "react-notifications" import { useParams, useNavigate, Link as RouterLink } from "react-router-dom" import {Button, Card, CardActions, CardContent, Table, TableBody, TableCell, TableRow, Typography} from "@mui/material"; export const PatientsDetails = () => { const { patientId } = useParams() const navigate = useNavigate() const [patient, setPatient] = useState( null ) //set to null & remove mock data // { // "id": "201728560", // "name": "Taylor Alison Swift", // "birth": "13.12.89", // "iin": "131289898989", // "blood": "2", // "emergency": "87777777777", // "contact": "87777777777", // "email": "tt.swift@gmail.com", // "address": "Kabanbay batyr, 53", // "marital": "not married", // "registered_date": "31.10.22" // } // ) // !!! UNCOMMENT useEffect(() => { if (patientId) { PatientApi .getPatientById(patientId) .then((patient, error) => { if (error) { NotificationManager.error(error) } else { console.log(patient); setPatient(patient) } }) .catch(console.error) } // eslint-disable-next-line react-hooks/exhaustive-deps }, [patientId]) return ( patient && (
{patient.name} Patient ID {patient.id} IIN {patient.iinNum} Birth date {patient.dateOfBirth} Blood type {patient.bloodGroup} Emergency number {patient.emerContactNum} Contact number {patient.contactNum} {/* Emergency number {patient.emergency} */} Email {patient.email} Address {patient.address} Marital status {patient.maritalSts} Registered date {patient.created_at}
) ) }
